#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.84:0.2"
msgid "8. Vinayavagga "
msgstr "8. The Monastic Law "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.84:0.3"
msgid "84. Adhikaraṇasamathasutta "
msgstr "84. Settlement of Disciplinary Issues "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.144, sc1
msgctxt "an7.84:1.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhikkhave, adhikaraṇasamathā dhammā uppannuppannānaṃ adhikaraṇānaṃ samathāya vūpasamāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these seven principles for the settlement of any disciplinary issues that might arise. "

msgctxt "an7.84:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

#. VAR: paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ dātabbaṃ, yebhuyyasikā dātabbā, tassapāpiyasikā dātabbā, tiṇavatthārako dātabbo → paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ, yebhuyyasikā, tassa pāpiyasikā, tiṇavatthārako (syā1-3) 2V:2094 vinayena ca 8D:1021 saṅgītisuttena ca
msgctxt "an7.84:1.3"
msgid "Sammukhāvinayo dātabbo, sativinayo dātabbo, amūḷhavinayo dātabbo, paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ dātabbaṃ, yebhuyyasikā dātabbā, tassapāpiyasikā dātabbā, tiṇavatthārako dātabbo. "
msgstr "Removal in the presence of those concerned is applicable. Removal by accurate recollection is applicable. Removal due to recovery from madness is applicable. The acknowledgement of the offense is applicable. The decision of a majority is applicable. A verdict of aggravated misconduct is applicable. Covering over with grass is applicable. "

msgctxt "an7.84:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta adhikaraṇasamathā dhammā uppannuppannānaṃ adhikaraṇānaṃ samathāya vūpasamāyā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the seven principles for the settlement of any disciplinary issues that might arise.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.84:1.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.84:1.6"
msgid "Vinayavaggo aṭṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.84:2.1"
msgid "Caturo vinayadharā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.84:2.2"
msgid "caturo ceva sobhanā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.84:2.3"
msgid "Sāsanaṃ adhikaraṇa—"
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.84:2.4"
msgid "samathenaṭṭhame dasāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
